INSTALLING PREREQUISITES:

Node Version Manager - Node.js and npm
First go to https://nodejs.org/en/ and find the version number of the LTS.

https://github.com/creationix/nvm
Install Script: get updated script url from install page.
curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.29.0/install.sh | bash
Close and re-open your terminal
nvm install 4.2.3
nvm use 4.2.3
nvm alias default 4.2.3


Ruby - Needed for SASS
sudo apt-get install ruby-full


SASS
Already Installed:
sudo gem update sass

New Install:
http://sass-lang.com/install
sudo gem install sass


GIT
sudo apt-get install git


Gulp
https://github.com/gulpjs/gulp/blob/master/docs/getting-started.md
npm install --global gulp


Bower
http://bower.io/#install-bower
npm install -g bower


GETTING STARTED:

Start a new project
src
build

Open a terminal and type: bower init (help: https://github.com/bower/spec/blob/master/json.md)
Install package and add it to bower.json dependencies:
bower install <package> --save

Bootstrap:
http://getbootstrap.com/
bower install bootstrap --save
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/bower_components/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/bower_components/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">

AngularJS:
bower install angular#1.4.8 --save
<script src="/bower_components/angular/angular.min.js"></script>

Angular Local Storage:
https://github.com/grevory/angular-local-storage
bower install angular-local-storage --save
<script src="/bower_components/angular-local-storage/dist/angular-local-storage.min.js"></script>
angular.module: 'LocalStorageModule'

AngularUI Router:
https://github.com/angular-ui/ui-router
bower install angular-ui-router --save
<script src="/bower_components/angular-ui-router/release/angular-ui-router.min.js"></script>
angular.module: 'ui.bootstrap'

AngularCSS: 
Requires AngularUI Router
https://github.com/castillo-io/angular-css
bower install angular-css --save
<script src="/bower_components/angular-css/angular-css.min.js"></script>
angular.module: 'door3.css'

AngularUI UI Bootstrap:
https://angular-ui.github.io/bootstrap/
bower install angular-bootstrap --save
<script src="/bower_components/angular-bootstrap/ui-bootstrap-tpls.min.js"></script>
angular.module: 'ui.bootstrap'

Highcharts + Angular Highcharts-ng
http://www.highcharts.com/
https://github.com/pablojim/highcharts-ng
bower install highcharts-release --save
bower install highcharts-ng --save
<script src="/bower_components/highcharts/highcharts.js"></script>
<script src="/bower_components/highcharts/adapters/standalone-framework.js"></script>
<script src="/bower_components/highcharts/modules/exporting.js"></script>  <!- Load additional modules if necessary
<script src="/bower_components/highcharts/themes/dark-unica.js"></script>  <!- Load a theme if necessary
<script src="/bower_components/highcharts-ng/dist/highcharts-ng.min.js"></script>
angular.module: 'highcharts-ng'

AngularUI Grid
http://ui-grid.info/
https://github.com/angular-ui/ui-grid
bower install angular-ui-grid --save
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/bower_components/angular-ui-grid/ui-grid.min.css">
<script src="/bower_components/angular-ui-grid/ui-grid.min.js">
angular.module: 'ui.grid'


Additional Resources:
AngularUI - http://angular-ui.github.io/
Bower Search: http://bower.io/search/

